  <brief_title>Prevention of Missed Opportunities for HIV Diagnosis by Promoting HIV Testing of Patients With Pneumococcal Pneumonia at Nice University Hospital (PneumoVIH)</brief_title>
  <acronym>PneumoVIH</acronym>
